OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FPolice missed an opportunity to arrest
OL,7,FValdo Calocane after he attacked his
OL,8,Fcolleagues at a warehouse, a month
OL,9,Fbefore the Nottingham attacks.
OL,11,FCalocane - who killed three people in
OL,12,Fthe 2023 Nottingham attacks - was
OL,13,Fwanted under an arrest warrant issued
OL,14,Fnearly a year before the murders.
OL,16,FAnd just a month before, he attacked
OL,17,Ftwo people while working at a
OL,18,Fwarehouse near Kegworth in
OL,19,FLeicestershire.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FBut Leicestershire Police at the time
OL,7,Ffailed to spot his arrest warrant.
OL,9,FHe went on to stab University of
OL,10,FNottingham students Barnaby Webber and
OL,11,FGrace O'Malley-Kumar and school
OL,12,Fcaretaker Ian Coates. He tried to kill
OL,13,Fthree more people in the early hours
OL,14,Fof 13 June 2023.
OL,16,FHe was originally wanted by police in
OL,17,FSeptember 2022 after being charged
OL,18,Fwith assaulting an emergency worker,
OL,19,Fbut failed to appear in court.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FNearly a year later, on 5 May 2023, he
OL,7,Fpunched a male colleague in the face
OL,8,Fand pushed over a female co-worker,
OL,9,Finjuring her knee.
OL,11,FPC Libbie-Mae Taylor, who attended the
OL,12,Fscene, said she was fairly new and was
OL,13,Fbeing supervised by a more experienced
OL,14,Fofficer.
OL,16,FAn audit of Leicestershire Police
OL,17,Fcomputer records showed that weeks
OL,18,Flater, PC Taylor clicked twice on
OL,19,Frecords that showed Calocane was
OL,20,Falready wanted.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FThe officer said she should have gone
OL,7,Fto the warehouse to chase up the
OL,8,Faccounts of victims.
OL,10,FShe said of the computer records: "If
OL,11,FI did click on it then I have not
OL,12,Fabsorbed that information.
OL,14,F"It's a simple task that should have
OL,15,Fbeen done and it wasn't and it was a
OL,16,Fmistake.
OL,26,@rD@cOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"I think in this incident I made
OL,7,Fmistakes. I think that we've all
OL,8,Fadmitted... accepted that we've made
OL,9,Fthese mistakes. I can only apologise
OL,10,Ffor making those mistakes."
OL,12,FAfter it was put to her that "right
OL,13,Ffrom the beginning" there had been an
OL,14,Fopportunity, given what was on police
OL,15,Frecords, to have arrested Calocane,
OL,16,Fshe added: "I accept that I didn't
OL,17,Flook and it was a missed opportunity."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@[O]tD@^OUuD@SO]xD@LOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FPC Taylor also said she had "docked"
OL,7,Fbut not saved body-worn video, which
OL,8,Fincluded Calocane's colleagues'
OL,9,Finitial accounts.
OL,11,FWhen asked why her body-worn footage
OL,12,Fhad not been saved, PC Taylor told the
OL,13,Finquiry: "I think, at the time, I was
OL,14,Ftoo literal in thinking it's not
OL,15,Fevidential because it didn't show
OL,16,Fanything."
OL,18,FShe said she was unaware that "docked"
OL,19,Ffootage was deleted after 31 days and
OL,20,F"unfortunately that's what happened".
OL,26,@nD@]OUnD@dO]uD@JOUxD@JO]zD@_OUzD@fO]|D@
OL,26,AAOU|D@dO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,FPC Taylor's superviser, PC Connor Amos-
OL,7,FPerkins, admitted he should have
OL,8,F"double-checked" Calocane's background.
OL,10,FThe inquiry was told that if body-worn
OL,11,Fvideo footage was not marked as being
OL,12,Fevidential, it was automatically wiped
OL,13,Ffrom police systems after a month.
OL,15,FTemporary Police Sergeant Mark Read,
OL,16,Fof Leicestershire Police, said: "If I
OL,17,Fhad done checks sooner I would have
OL,18,Fensured that the body cam would have
OL,19,Fbeen marked as evidential.
OL,26,@xD@aOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/9
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,379,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1773493904
OL,3,CPolice failed to arrest Valdo Calocane
OL,4,Ca month before Nottingham attacks
OL,6,F"Officers do sometimes forget to mark
OL,7,Fit as evidential. I have come across
OL,8,Fit before."
OL,10,FCalocane, who admitted manslaughter
OL,11,Fand attempted murder, is detained
OL,12,Findefinitely in a high-security
OL,13,Fhospital after prosecutors accepted
OL,14,Fhis not guilty pleas to murder.
OL,16,FHe was sentenced at Nottingham Crown
OL,17,FCourt in January 2024.
OL,19,FThe inquiry continues.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
